We study a highly simplified scenario of viral replication that includes intra- and inter-host dynamics (cf. Fig. 3). The link between the two is established by a transmission model, which, following Lange and Ferguson (2009), leads us to quantifying viral fitness in terms of a version of the basic reproduction number \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
